      "comment": "ART OF DECEPTION (1) has been hard to follow lately, running fourth (22.04) last time but prior to that ran very well when placed at this track. Expecting sharp improvement this line-up. DISTANCE DRUMS (2) scored a most impressive win two back then drifted back and missed the frame latest finishing a 7 length 5th at Q Parklands (30.27). Has ability and is one of the better chances. HARA'S MILLY (5) missed the frame last time but had been racing well prior to that, winning a Grade 5 three back before a placing at Q Parklands the following run. Rates a winning chance on best. OLIVER GO (8) showed good early speed and won last start. Must be respected.",
